器脱落<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/virgin-orbit-update-cause-start-me-up-mission-failure-191641002.html">而失败</a>。该公司在 3 月份开始<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/virgin-orbit-furloughs-most-employees-and-pauses-operations-for-a-week-065542834.html">“暂停运营”</a> ，作为在<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/virgin-orbit-files-for-bankruptcy-protection-as-it-seeks-a-buyer-094236877.html">申请破产保护</a>并最终<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/virgin-orbit-officially-shutters-its-space-launch-operations-231755999.html">在几周后认输</a>之前寻找新投资者的最后一口气。</p><p>与此同时，总部位于德克萨斯州雪松公园<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/nasa-firefly-aerospace-contract-175129610.html">的 Firefly Aerospace</a>正在开发一种名为 Firefly Alpha 的运载火箭。这种两级液体燃料火箭设计用于从不同地点发射。它的第一次尝试在 2021 年失败了，但火箭在次年部分成功地进行了轨道发射。该公司预计将第三次为美国太空部队发射。</p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/firefly-aerospace-buys-the-final-scraps-of-doomed-virgin-orbit-193049970.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/firefly-aerospace-buys-the-final-scraps-of-doomed-virgin-orbit-193049970.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 8a83b550-72f3-4075-88a9-e184a8336b46</guid><dc:creator>威尔尚克林</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Fri, 16 Jun 2023 19:30:49 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686941577</ingested><modified> 2023-06-16T18:53:01+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Industrials]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="2400" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/4a6a2000-0c75-11ee-9d7b-b30a58df9b8c" width="3600"><med